37:36.297 --> 37:37.938
Mom, why are you crying?

37:38.498 --> 37:43.208
Why are you crying, Mom? Don't cry.

37:43.478 --> 37:45.708
I'm sorry...

37:46.748 --> 37:48.148
I'm sorry...

37:48.978 --> 37:50.277
I won't cry.

37:50.447 --> 37:51.478
